<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望悟空可以找到很多食物。”八戒说，“我饿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧打了个寒颤，蜷缩着身体。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太冷了。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又抬头看了看那庙，然后又看了看他的徒弟们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们两个也觉得那里有妖怪吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净摸了摸下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不确定，但悟空说有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒哼了一声。“悟空过于小心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他总是担心我们会遇到妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的肚子又咕咕地叫了起来。“我饿死了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净又看了看那庙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得那庙看上去挺安全的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒点点头。“那里看上去也很温暖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许那里的和尚会让我们进去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果可以取暖，那就太好了。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就这么定了。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁管那猴子想什么！他知道什么啊？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们到那庙里取取暖，再吃点儿东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧上了马。三个人朝着庙的方向走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们到庙门口的时候，发现周围一个人都没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里被废弃了。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒敲了敲门，但没人回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人吗？”八戒喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人吗？”依然没人回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒看着唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许里面的和尚没听到我的声音。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的眼睛突然亮了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许他们正在厨房里做饭呢！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>煮面，炒菜，厨房里一定很吵。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒的肚子又咕咕地叫了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要进去看看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒打开门走了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>庙里又黑又安静。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没听到做饭的声音。”八戒自言自语道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许里面真的没有人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走过了一条长长的走廊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>走廊两侧有很多漆黑的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人吗？”他又喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，他看见一个房间里有亮光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他走了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阳光从窗外射了进来，正好照亮了一张桌子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>桌子上有三件背心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“背心看上去很华丽。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打了个冷颤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们看上去也很暖和。”他四下看了看，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>迅速抓起背心冲到了外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“里面没人。”八戒对唐僧和悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我找到了这些背心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！”悟净拿了一件背心说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我快冻死了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒也递给了唐僧一件。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧皱着眉头说：“我不会穿的。这是你偷来的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没偷。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我......我是借的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧瞪着八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你必须立刻把这些背心还回去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以在离开之前把背心还回去啊。”悟净提议说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对吧，八戒？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然啦！”八戒说，“我们会还回去的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们两个太坏了。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你们偷东西，我们就永远不能从佛祖那里取得真经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒耸耸肩。“师父，你可以不穿，但我很冷。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举起一只手臂穿过了袖洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净也穿上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283806</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒又把另一只手穿了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净开始扣背心的扣子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他们开始大叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好紧啊！”八戒大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能呼吸了！”悟净大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们倒在了地上，拼命想把背心脱下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这背心脱不掉了！”八戒大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是谁偷了我的背心？”一个声音高叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个长着巨大角的妖怪冲了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看八戒和悟净，然后又转向了唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”妖怪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我......我来自大唐。”唐僧哆嗦着回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去西天......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪握起了双手。“你是唐僧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>